data.description: Meticulously maintained and upgraded this custom home was built by & for a builder. The double-wall construction & insulation creates a peaceful sanctuary for audiophiles! No outside noise gets in & inside you have a Dolby Almos Home Theater 12-speakers, Marantz SR-8515 receiver, IYKYK. LG OLED TVs, 77” & 65” in master. Hardwood floors. Solid wood doors. Custom carpets. This home is offered furnished w/high quality furnishings, linens & upgraded appliances, chefs kitchen, soft close cabinets/drawers, dinnerware/glassware/utensils, everything you need… down to the Christmas tree! Luxurious leather seating. Most furnishings new in last 3 years. Lime, orange, avocado, mango trees in private orchard. White pineapple & more in mature garden. 1000+ sf covered lanai w/ dinning & seating to enjoy best of Hawaii’s climate & sunsets. Downstairs updated outdoor space complete w/ gym, ping pong, darts & more. Sheer amount of enclosed, protected storage below is unmatched. Cul-de-sac entry & green space behind offer the ultimate privacy. 2-car garage. Not a cookie-cutter kit house. Enjoy luxury from day one in this turn-key home. By appointment only.  “All comments, data is provided by seller or seller's representatives. Buyer to confirm all & hold all parties harmless from any discrepancy data in the mls and advertising. Limited Service–Data Entry Addendum signed by seller/s must be sign by buyer/s with Purchase Contract."
